# ScaleBuds Marketing — `home-services-niche-guide` (complete handoff)

## Product & outputs
- **Brand:** ScaleBuds Marketing — home services marketing (HVAC, plumbing, roofing, electrical, remodel, etc.).
- **Live:** Vercel production alias [home-services-niche-guide.vercel.app](https://home-services-niche-guide.vercel.app); custom domain **scalebuds.com** when DNS points to the same Vercel project.
- **GitHub:** `nabilakhannn/home-services-niche-guide`, branch `main`.

## Stack (this app only)
- **Vite 7** + **React 19** + **Wouter** + **Tailwind v4** — app root `client/src/`, entry `client/src/main.tsx`, routes `client/src/App.tsx`.
- **SSR/static:** Express `server/index.ts` serves `dist/public` in Node; **Vercel** uses `vercel.json` (SPA rewrites excluding `/api/*`, `outputDirectory: dist/public`) + **`api/submit-lead.ts`** serverless for `POST /api/submit-lead`.
- **Build:** `pnpm run build` — Vite → `dist/public`, esbuild bundles `server/index.ts` → `dist/index.js`, **`index.html` copied to `404.html`** for client-side routes.
- **Dev:** Vite + `server/vite-plugin-submit-lead.ts` (mirrors submit-lead API); env from `.env` via `vite.config.ts` `loadEnv`.

## GoHighLevel / Lead Connector (leads)
- **Inbound webhook URL** (example; confirm in `.env.example` / Vercel):  
  `https://services.leadconnectorhq.com/hooks/Pglkea64yintAtcVebhi/webhook-trigger/wcaMlNw5BRX1OZxwDxOX`
- **Env (set in Vercel + local `.env`):**
  - `GHL_INBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL` — full POST target for leads.
  - `GHL_PIPELINE_ID` — `pit-9065baee-ac4a-43d5-883b-2744f85d6830` (pipeline id, **not** a Private Integration API token).
  - `GHL_LOCATION_ID` — `Pglkea64yintAtcVebhi` (sent as `locationId` + `ghlLocationId` in JSON).
  - Optional: `GHL_PRIVATE_INTEGRATION_TOKEN` — only for future server-side HighLevel REST scripts; never browser.
- **Payload:** `lib/leadApi.ts` → **`buildGhlPayload()`** — **flat JSON only** (no nested `contact` object). Includes `source: "scalebuds-website"`, optional `pipelineId` / `locationId` / `ghlPipelineId` / `ghlLocationId`, plus `formId`, `email`, names, `phone`, `companyName`, `niche`, `service`, `message`, `smsConsent`, **`smsMarketingConsent`**, **`smsTransactionalConsent`**, `pageUrl`, `submittedAt`.
- **`api/submit-lead.ts`:** Duplicate of parse/build/forward logic — **must stay aligned** with `lib/leadApi.ts` when fields change (Vercel bundler).
- **Forwarder:** `forwardToGhl()` — `POST`, `Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8`.
- **Testing webhook:** Use **POST** with JSON. Opening the webhook URL in a **browser** (GET, no body) returns GHL “invalid body” — expected.
- **Client:** `client/src/lib/submitLead.ts` → `POST /api/submit-lead`.

