## Homepage (`client/src/pages/Home.tsx`) — notable UI
- **Hero image:** `HERO_IMG` CDN (CloudFront/Manus asset). Stock photo may show non–ScaleBuds shirt branding.
- **Shirt fix:** Absolute **opaque ScaleBuds badge** over chest (large `rgba(11,18,32,0.98)` panel, **Scale** + orange **Buds**). **Responsive:** `max-sm` anchored `left-[4%]`; **`md+`** `md:right-[clamp(7%,11vw,20%)]` — covers typical “left chest” logo placement; tweak if crop changes.
- **Hero** dark gradient overlay on image.
- **Section order:** Hero → **stats bar** ($189K / 62% / 5 min / 24/7, `Counter` with optional `$` prefix) → **`IndustriesMarquee`** (“Industries We Serve” infinite ticker) → `HvacDualRealityShowcase` → three pillars → problem section → …
- **`IndustriesMarquee`:** Ten trade labels; CSS **`animate-industries-marquee`** in `client/src/index.css` (`@keyframes industries-marquee`, `prefers-reduced-motion` wraps).
- **LeadCaptureBand** on home: email-only; helper text points to contact page / email (no chat).

## Forms & compliance copy
- **`Contact.tsx`:** Compliance-style form — **Full Name**, **Email** (required), **Phone**; separate **marketing** and **transactional** SMS consent checkboxes + Terms/Privacy links; blue **Submit**; `formId: "contact-sms-compliance"`; `smsConsent` true if either SMS box is checked; phone required (10+ digits) when any SMS box is checked.
- **`LeadCapturePopup` / `LeadCaptureBand`:** Email-focused; short forms on home/modals.
- **`client/src/config/businessContact.ts`:** Legal entity line, address, **email** for footer/legal.
- **Privacy / Terms:** **Last updated** see files — **Contact page** may collect phone + SMS opt-ins; **SMS also via chat widget** or other disclosed programs.

